# FILE: adminDashboard/libraryManager/libraryManager.desc
# ROLE: Digital Asset Indexer & Metadata Terminal
# ROUTE: /admin/library
# ACCOUNT: Admin only
# THEME: Dark · link management · monospace table · bulk-check tools

## 1. EXTERNAL LINK TERMINAL (No local file hosting)
- INPUT FIELDS:
  - Google Drive ID: paste unique doc ID (e.g., "1A2b3C4d...")
  - Thumbnail URL: cover image link (Cloudinary or Drive)
  - [🔍 اختبار الرابط] button — verifies file is publicly viewable before saving
- VALIDATION: highlights row in rose if link is broken/private

## 2. METADATA BENTO
- CATEGORY: 🏗️ الهندسة · 🏥 الطب · ⚖️ الحقوق · 🎨 الفنون · 💻 التقنية
- YEAR: dropdown (1–5 + دراسات عليا)
- TERM: الأول / الثاني
- TYPE: 📚 كتاب · 📝 ملخص · 🔬 بحث · 🎓 نموذج امتحان
- DESCRIPTION: textarea for brief abstract

## 3. NATIVE VS. CONTRIBUTOR TOGGLE
- 🏠 منصة (Native): platform-curated content
- 🤝 مساهم (Student-contributed): shows contributor name/ID from student profile
  - Contributor's profile linked in /library/viewer document footer

## 4. LIVE REPOSITORY TABLE
- STYLE: bg-[#0F1828] · border · rounded-2xl · monospace rows
- COLUMNS: #LIB-ID · Title · External Link · Access Count · Visibility
- VISIBILITY: [👁️ عام] | [🔒 مخفي] — toggle per document

## 5. BULK LINK CHECKER
- [🔍 فحص جميع الروابط] button — pings all Drive IDs
- Result: rose highlight on any broken/revoked link

## 6. ACTIONS
- [➕ إضافة مستند جديد] — opens form
- Quick search by faculty or keyword
